title: New breakthrough in Taiwan. Fighter ADF is going to push the sales of the F-35 to Taiwan.
description:
#chinainsights#fifthgenerationaircraft#taiwan#fighter
New breakthrough in Taiwan: The prototype of the ADF "Advanced Defense Fighter" is about to debut, and the fuselage configuration has passed the wind tunnel test! Its capability surpasses South Korea's KF-21! The engine is the procured F414 or homemade Vega engine? ADF is aiming to meet the standards of the fifth-generation aircraft. ADF is going to push the sales of the F-35 to Taiwan.
